Kupocard Mini 2 Returns!

Until Sat., Oct. 31, at 01:59 UTC

The Kupocard Mini 2 returns again for the Autumn Festival!

You may purchase the Kupocard Mini 2 up to 6 times during this campaign to receive a total of 21,000 Gems!

It will be available for purchase until Sat., Oct. 31, at 01:59 UTC, so don't miss out!

Kupocard Mini 2


Kupocard Mini 2
  • Initial reward: 1,050 Gems
  • Daily reward: 350 Gems (for 7 days)
  • Total: 3,500 Gems

You can purchase the Kupocard Mini 2 alongside the Kupocard Mini.

About Kupocard Minis

Upon purchasing the Kupocard Mini 2, you will receive the initial reward immediately, and the daily reward will be sent to your Gift Box alongside your daily bonus from your next login, for a total of 7 logins.

After receiving the seventh daily reward, you can purchase another Kupocard Mini 2 and/or another Kupocard Mini as long as it is within the campaign period. This means you can purchase up to 6 Kupocards (each) during this period!

* Logins do not need to be consecutive for you to receive all 7 login bonuses.
* Login bonuses reset at 08:00 UTC.
* You can confirm how many logins remain on your Kupocard(s) by tapping on the "Kupocards" button on the Gifts screen.
* If you have a currently active Kupocard Mini or Kupocard Mini 2 from a previous sale, you will be unable to purchase another of the same type until after receiving its seventh daily reward.
* Previous sale duration: Jul. 1, 2020, at 02:00 – Jul. 29, 2020, at 01:59 UTC
